                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>Hello {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Please follow these instructions carefully when self-administering CJC-1295/Ipamorelin:&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step 1: Flip off colored plastic cap/tear off center seal from the CJC-1295/Ipamorelin vial and wipe the top with alcohol swab.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step 2: Remove cap from the provided water and wipe the top with alcohol swab.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step 3: Using the mixing syringe, turn the bottle of water upside down and insert the needle and &lt;strong&gt;draw 5ml of water.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step 4: Remove the syringe from vial with Bacteriostatic Water and inject slowly into the CJC/Ipamorelin powder.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step 5: Swirl the vial around until solution is clear.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Step 6: Discard any Bacteriostatic Water left from the original Bacteriostatic Water vial and &lt;strong&gt;refrigerate CJC-1295/Ipamorelin after reconstitution.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
** Please note that each time prior to inserting the syringe into the CJC-1295/Ipamorelin vial you should always wipe the top of the vial first**&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;This is a subcutaneous injection. Injection sites include any fatty area located in the: &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; Abdominal/hip area [preferable location to inject]&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Tricep area [must be done by someone else]&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Anterior Thigh [alternative site]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
**Fats and carbs may blunt the effect of this medication. Always inject on an empty stomach. Wait at least 30 - 60 minutes after injecting to ingest fats/carbs. Protein is okay. If injecting before bed, no fats/carbs for at least 2 hours prior to injecting, this includes alcohol **&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Please reach out if you have any questions or concerns.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Yours in health,&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The Team at &lt;strong&gt;10&lt;span style=&quot;color:#c0392b;&quot;&gt;X&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; Health&lt;br /&gt;
Phone: {!Account.OwnerPhone&lt;br /&gt;
Main: &lt;a href=&quot;tel: 305.682.1818&quot;&gt;305.682.1818&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Fax: 786.598.8612&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.10xhealthsystem.com&quot;&gt;10xhealthsystem.com&lt;/a&gt;</value>
